Actor and presenter Sthembiso Khoza, popularly known as SK Khoza, is smitten with his girlfiend Pabee Moganedi. The actor who's for his role on Mzansi Magic's soapie The Queen took to Instagram to share a heartfelt letter to his bae. The star began his post by expressing his love for her and how he feels whenever he is around her. "The way you look at me, makes me feel like I'm the only person in the world. With you I can be myself, I love that we are also friends at the same time. When we're together, all my problems disappear," he wrote. ALSO READ: WATCH: SK KHOZA TRYING HIS LUCK IN MUSIC! SK, who has been dating his actress girlfriend Pabee for more than a year now, further wrote he is grateful for the support she has shown him since the beginning of their relationship. "You’re always there for me, no matter what. You let me be myself and you encourage me to find more of myself.'' The entertainment industry comes with a lot of disappointments at times and SK acknowledges this. He said he's grateful to have someone in his life who encourages him whenever he feels like he has failed. "You encourage me after I feel like I’ve failed. You make me feel like I can get through anything, as long as I have you. You sacrifice and work so hard, without even realising that you are," he wrote. The way you look at me, makes me feel like I'm the only person in the world. With you I can be myself. I love that we are also friends at the same time. When we're together, all my problems disappear. You make my heart smile. You know me better than I know myself...You’re always there for me, no matter what. You let me be myself and you encourage me to find more of myself. You are truthful and vulnerable with me. You encourage me after I feel like I’ve failed. You make me feel like I can get through anything, as long as I have you. You sacrifice and work so hard, without even realizing that you are. A post shared by  Sthembiso Khoza (@skcoza) on Feb 6, 2020 at 8:02am PST   